| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1996 — Recovery Inhibition (karakurt)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 934e8f0d-77e8-5dc9-8906-e1e85bb687ab"
